{"tid":2134600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市傳微軟正洽購抖音Tiktok","createTime":"2020-07-31T23:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:39:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba5964ef3fd4d46ecba6a580732af39603fb42c","tid":2134600,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，美國總統川普31日表示，正在考慮對抖音的中國母公司字節跳動科技（ByteDance）採取不同的措施，包括禁用抖音，也可能採取其他措施。多家外媒指出，川普政府可能會要求字節跳動科技出售抖音在美國的業務，潛在買家則是微軟，雙邊正洽談收購事宜。<br />\n<br />\n對此消息，抖音表示不對猜測發表評論，並對抖音的長期成功充滿信心，微軟則拒絕回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3246368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3246368&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=982eabbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3246368&h=ec53e215\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3246368</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/31/microsoft-is-reportedly-in-talks-to-buy-social-app-tiktok.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F07%2F31%2Fmicrosoft-is-reportedly-in-talks-to-buy-social-app-tiktok.html&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=3bad75ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/07/31/microsoft-is-reportedly-in-talks-to-buy-social-app-tiktok.html</a>"},{"pid":"7c7371c521c0821c1404b1d6e71f6d7e7b06a3f2","tid":2134600,"uid":39365,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"我覺得微軟係幫抖音過骨，買左後照樣俾中國控制"},{"pid":"e08765cc57d80d15e4f5d45442077ce77a43bcb3","tid":2134600,"uid":32722,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:01:45.000Z","msg":"bill gates 又一操控人心智既工具"},{"pid":"d4f96902ec66369d99e2108c413127af641a7d3b","tid":2134600,"uid":50124,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e08765cc57d80d